% ══════════════════════════════════════════════
% PHRASE 2 — bars 5–9
% Full 8 voices; bar 5 beat 4: G# (original) replaced with G (diatonic)
% ══════════════════════════════════════════════
%
% V5 (T1) bar 5: original ^G, replaced by G natural on beat 4
% Bar 6: original tenor G, whole note (unaltered, G is diatonic)
% Bar 6 harmony: A major pedal (diatonic V chord); tenor E3 and C#3 used
%
